track_notes:
summer ascent
try from April to November
distance one way: 5km
elevation gain: 850m

Beware: between trackpoint No.138 and No.158 the track is calculated. The track several times is not visable and no signs between these two points. At trackpoint No.138 you see a lonley foresters house. From here to the summit the track is fine but often wet and muddy.
Parking is free, but the toll road costs 2EUR.
Pictures you may find here: 
http://42u.de/v/Gunnar/sota/2015-10-26-baumgartenschneid/
Nice tour from Spitzingsattel to Bodenschneid to Spitzingsee
